                            <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/486">Syria</placeName>,
                            <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/716">Arabia</placeName>,
                            <placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/109">Callinicus</placeName>, selling everything that they owned. </desc>
                    </event>
