                                sisters</persName>presided over a <placeName
                                ref="http://syriaca.org/place/2828"
                                >monastery</placeName>in<placeName
                                ref="http://syriaca.org/place/2827">N'ns</placeName>, in the region
                                of<placeName ref="http://syriaca.org/place/2758"
